<h1>Settings for <%= @user.name %></h1>

Gonna put some settings in here...<br>
<%= form_tag '/settings' %>
    On the profile page...
    Statistics visible to                 <%= select_tag "statistics",  privacy_options(@settings[0]) %> <br>
    Networks visible to                   <%= select_tag "networks",    privacy_options(@settings[1]) %> <br>
    Hottest Friends visible to            <%= select_tag "hottest",     privacy_options(@settings[2]) %> <br>
    Facebook Link visible to              <%= select_tag "facebook",    privacy_options(@settings[3]) %> <br>

    Profile can show up on rankings for   <%= select_tag "rankings",    privacy_options(@settings[4]) %> <br>

    Other Settings...
    Send email when friend joins:         <%= check_box_tag "email_friend_joins", "allowed", @other_settings[0] != 0 %> <br>
    Send updates(newsletter):             <%= check_box_tag "email_newsletter",   "allowed", @other_settings[1] != 0 %> <br>
                                          <%= hidden_field_tag 'update', true %>
    <%= submit_tag "Save Settings" %><br>
